This paper deals with the allocation of inventory for online graphical display advertising, which involves optimization and decision-making processes. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Mathematical Optimization (cs.MA), and Game Theory (cs.GT) sub-categories.
